Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value:
BEGIN
WITH [CTE](Id, ParentId, BlobLink, BlobThumbnail) AS ( SELECT Id, ParentId, BlobLink, BlobThumbnail FROM FileSystem fs WHERE (fs.Id = @Id)
UNION ALL
SELECT fs.Id, fs.ParentId, fs.BlobLink, fs.BlobThumbnail FROM FileSystem fs INNER JOIN [CTE] p ON fs.ParentId = p.Id )
--DELETE FROM FileSystem --WHERE Id IN( -- SELECT t.Id -- FROM [CTE] t)
SELECT t.Id, t.BlobLink, t.BlobThumbnail FROM [CTE] t
OPTION ( MAXRECURSION 0 )
END

Property.Name: BodyScript
Property.Value: begin delete fs from FileSystem fs left join (select Id from deleted) d on fs.Id = d.Id where fs.ParentId = d.Id end
